Usage: write_oa_techfile [-help] [<fileName>] [-include_rules]
                         [-process_node <coord>]

-help                 # Prints out the command usage
<fileName>            # output ASCII filename (string, optional)
-include_rules        # include LDRS and VIA information (bool, optional)
-process_node <coord> # specify process node value(in nm) (int, optional)